---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Pierce Moore — Ask"
  description="Query interface coming in v2. For now, see the FAQ on the home page."
>
  <section class="page-gutter pt-32 pb-24 max-w-prose">
    <div class="label-mono mb-3">/ ask</div>
    <h1 class="display-roman text-3xl text-ink leading-tight">query interface — coming in v2.</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-base text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
      A live, model-backed interface that answers questions about my work,
      experience, and opinions is planned for v2 of this site. Until then,
      the FAQ on the home page is the static version.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/#faq" class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-accent border border-[color:var(--accent-dim)] px-4 py-2 hover:border-[color:var(--accent)]">read the faq →</a>
      <a href="/" class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-ink-muted border border-[color:var(--hairline)] px-4 py-2 hover:border-[color:var(--ink-muted)]">← return home</a>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-12 font-mono text-xs text-ink-dim">
      <span class="text-accent">$ </span>curl -X POST {Astro.site}api/ask &nbsp;<span class="text-ink-faint"># returns 501 until v2</span>
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
